<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help & Guidance - QueuePro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #3b82f6;
            --secondary-color: #1e3a8a;
            --bg-light: #f8fafc;
            --gray-600: #4b5563;
        }

        .help-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .help-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
        }

        .help-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .help-header p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* 4-Step Guidance */
        .guide-steps {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        .step-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border-color: #dbeafe;
        }

        .step-number {
            position: absolute;
            top: -20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }

        .step-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .step-card h3 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .step-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* FAQ Section */
        .faq-section {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 4rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .faq-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .faq-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .faq-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);
        }

        .faq-item h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .faq-item p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .cta-section .btn {
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .help-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .faq-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .faq-section {
                padding: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <div class="help-container">
            <div class="help-header">
                <h1>How It Works</h1>
                <p>Your simple 4-step guide to a faster, more efficient government office visit using QueuePro.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="guide-steps">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus step-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Register Account</h3>
                    <p>Create your secure account using your <strong>Mobile Number</strong> or
                        <strong>Username</strong>. This keeps your details ready for all future visits.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <i class="fas fa-list-check step-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Check Documents</h3>
                    <p>Select your service and review the <strong>Document Checklist</strong>. Ensure you have all
                        required originals to avoid rejection at the counter.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <i class="fas fa-ticket step-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Get Your Token</h3>
                    <p>Request a digital token. You'll instantly see your <strong>Token ID</strong>, queue position, and
                        <strong>Estimated Appointment Window</strong>.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <i class="fas fa-building-circle-check step-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Relax & Visit</h3>
                    <p>Monitor your status from home. Arrive at the office <strong>10 minutes before</strong> your time
                        window and present your digital token ID.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-section">
                <h2>Common Questions</h2>
                <div class="faq-grid">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>What if I'm late for my window?</h4>
                        <p>If you aren't present when your token is called, the officer will mark you as "missed". Your
                            token will be moved to a buffer zone for 15 minutes before expiring.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>Can I cancel my appointment?</h4>
                        <p>Yes, you can cancel your token anytime from your dashboard. This helps other citizens get
                            their service faster.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>Do I need to print the token?</h4>
                        <p>No printing is required. Simply show the digital token screen on your phone or provide your
                            Token ID to the officer.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>What are the office hours?</h4>
                        <p>The queue system follows standard government office hours (9:00 AM to 5:00 PM). Tokens cannot
                            be generated outside these hours.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="/citizen-dashboard" class="btn btn-primary"
                    style="background:var(--primary-color); color:white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration:none;">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left" style="margin-right:0.5rem;"></i> Back to Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>